    {
        "content": "<p>This works, thanks a lot!</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kd\">set_option</span> <span class=\"n\">old_structure_cmd</span> <span class=\"n\">true</span>\n<span class=\"kd\">structure</span> <span class=\"n\">iso</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">V</span> <span class=\"n\">W</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Type</span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">quiver</span> <span class=\"n\">V</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">quiver</span> <span class=\"n\">W</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n<span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">to_prefunctor</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">V</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚ü∂</span><span class=\"n\">q</span> <span class=\"n\">W</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n<span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">inv_prefunctor</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">W</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚ü∂</span><span class=\"n\">q</span> <span class=\"n\">V</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n<span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">left_inv</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">to_prefunctor</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚â´</span><span class=\"n\">q</span> <span class=\"n\">inv_prefunctor</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"mi\">ùüô</span><span class=\"n\">q</span> <span class=\"n\">V</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n<span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">right_inv</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">inv_prefunctor</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚â´</span><span class=\"n\">q</span> <span class=\"n\">to_prefunctor</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"mi\">ùüô</span><span class=\"n\">q</span> <span class=\"n\">W</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">structure</span> <span class=\"n\">cover_endo</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n<span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">to_prefunctor</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">U</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚ü∂</span><span class=\"n\">q</span> <span class=\"n\">U</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n<span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">cover</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">to_prefunctor</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚â´</span><span class=\"n\">q</span> <span class=\"n\">œÜ</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">œÜ</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">structure</span> <span class=\"n\">cover_auto</span> <span class=\"kd\">extends</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">iso</span> <span class=\"n\">U</span> <span class=\"n\">U</span><span class=\"o\">),</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">cover_endo</span> <span class=\"n\">œÜ</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
